Class MT5Service

Object
MT5Service
public class MT5Service extends Object
MT5 Service - High-level wrapper over MT5Account Provides a clean service layer with convenient methods that extract data from Reply objects. This is the recommended API for most applications - it hides gRPC complexity and provides simple return values. Architecture: - MT5Service (this class) - High-level convenience layer - MT5Account - Low-level gRPC client with automatic reconnection - gRPC stubs - Direct protocol buffer communication
